---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="About · NWAFU Scripts" lang="en" currentPath="/en/about/">
  <section class="hero page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About NWAFU Scripts</h1>
    <p>A userscript index for NWAFU-related websites.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="section prose">
    <p>NWAFU Scripts collects and publishes browser userscripts for campus-related websites. It keeps script notes, install URLs, and update URLs in one place.</p>
    <p>The project is personally maintained and is not an official university service. Each script detail page lists what the script does and which pages it matches.</p>
    <p>If a script stops working, the target page, API, or browser permissions may have changed. Report the page URL, browser version, userscript manager version, and any useful screenshots or console errors through <a href={`${siteConfig.repositoryUrl}/issues`}>GitHub Issues</a>.</p>
    <p>The site may load Google AdSense and Umami analytics. Umami is used to understand page visits; analytics do not affect how scripts run.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
